latex:
* Public git repo, where the source is available
* version of the program that is required for running the code
* Date when the pdf-file was generated
* parameters used (should get extracted from the Python program
    and no duplicate entry: once in tex file, once in the Python
    code.)
* Author name in the tex file as comment (and also as pdf-file content)
* At least two references, and coming from bib file only
